ProMED-mail
<promed@promedmail.org>
[Publications regarding _C. difficile_ have increased recently and have
been concerned primarily with 2 issues: the increased virulence of the
hyperproducer of toxin strains as reported above and the apparent
decreasing efficacy of metronidazole as a therapeutic modality. - Mod.LL]
